針對LGBT群體的負面刻板印象，通常有：戀愛關係欠缺穩定性、更可能[[濫交|濫交]]及虐待兒童，但這些宣稱都沒有得到科學證據支持。就戀愛關係的穩定度及忠誠度而言，同性伴侣跟異性伴侣之間基本沒有任何差别<ref name=amici2010/>。性傾向亦不是某人是否虐待兒童的影響因子<ref name=lamb>Michael Lamb, Ph.D.: [http://www.glad.org/uploads/docs/cases/gill-v-office-of-personnel-management/2009-11-17-doma-aff-lamb.pdf Affidavit – United States District Court for the District of Massachusetts (2009)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.glad.org/uploads/docs/cases/gill-v-office-of-personnel-management/2009-11-17-doma-aff-lamb.pdf |date=20101225193923 }}</ref><ref name=herekm>Gregory M. Herek, Ph.D.: [http://psychology.ucdavis.edu/rainbow/html/facts_molestation.html Facts About Homosexuality and Child Molestation] {{Wayback|url=http://psychology.ucdavis.edu/rainbow/html/facts_molestation.html |date=20100419022239 }}</ref><ref>American Psychological Association: [http://www.apa.org/pi/lgbt/resources/parenting-full.pdf Lesbian & Gay Parenting] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6cP5FBCRn?url=http://www.apa.org/pi/lgbt/resources/parenting-full.pdf |date=20151019203319 |dateformat=iso }}</ref>。現有科學證據證實「性傾向和[[兒童性騷擾|兒童性騷擾]]之間有關」的說法，是建立在術語誤用和失實的證據上<ref name="herekm"/><ref>{{cite web|author1=Jim Burroway|title=Are Gays A Threat To Our Children?|url=http://www.boxturtlebulletin.com/Articles/000,002.htm|website=Box Turtle Bulletin|access-date=2017-06-02|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211204308/http://www.boxturtlebulletin.com/Articles/000,002.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

