[[聯邦調查局|美國聯邦調查局]]（FBI）指出，2011年上報至美國執法機關的仇恨犯罪中，有20.4％出於性傾向偏見：其中有56.7％是出於針對男同性戀者的偏見；11.1％是出於針對女同性戀者的偏見；29.6％是出於不分性別的反同性戀偏見<ref name=fbicrime>{{citation |title=Victims |url=https://www.fbi.gov/about-us/cjis/ucr/hate-crime/2011/narratives/victims |periodical=[[联邦调查局|FBI]] |accessdate=2013-07-26 |archive-date=2016-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708091754/https://www.fbi.gov/about-us/cjis/ucr/hate-crime/2011/narratives/victims |dead-url=no }}</ref>。發生於1998年的[[馬修·謝巴德|馬修·謝巴德]]謀殺案便是一個著名的相關例子：谢巴德在事件中因他的同性戀傾向而遭謀殺<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.colby.edu/news/detail/612/|title=Mother of Hate-Crime Victim to Speak at Colby|publisher=Colby College|language=en|accessdate=2011-07-01|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629064716/http://www.colby.edu/news/detail/612/|archivedate=2011-06-29}}</ref>。此外他們亦有可能成為「矯正強姦」的受害者，其旨在以犯罪的方式把他們「矯正」為異性戀者。居住於某些地區的[[LGBT|LGBT]]群體亦有一定機會遭家屬殺害，行兇動機是「[[名譽殺人|保存自身家族的名聲]]」<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/honor-killings-target-turkeys-lgbt-community/ |title="Honor killings" target Turkey's LGBT community |publisher=CBS News |date=2011-10-12 |accessdate=2013-12-23 |archive-date=2021-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213215545/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/honor-killings-target-turkeys-lgbt-community/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Di Piero Russo |url=http://bari.repubblica.it/cronaca/2011/08/05/news/sei_il_disonore_della_famiglia-20061452/?ref=HREC2-6 |title="Sei il disonore della famiglia" e accoltella il fratello gay |publisher=bari.repubblica.it |accessdate=2013-12-23 |archive-date=2013-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224105154/http://bari.repubblica.it/cronaca/2011/08/05/news/sei_il_disonore_della_famiglia-20061452/?ref=HREC2-6 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/father-confesses-to-killing-his-own-son-in-landmark-homosexual-murder-case.aspx?PageID=238&NID=47579&NewsCatID=341 |title=Father confesses to killing 